  "riddle": "1. A payment pioneer began its journey in the year of establishment — can you unveil this moment in time?\n\n2. Discover how travelers rate the services of this renowned payment solutions provider. What is their score out of five?\n\n3. In the year you just uncovered, determine what day January 1st fell on — was it a Monday or perhaps a Sunday?\n\n4. Seek the city that stands as a financial hub and has a buzzing population; what number of residents called it home in the latest census?\n\n5. Ascend now to find how far above sea level this bustling capital rests — what is its elevation in meters?\n\n6. Count how many places of lodging can be found in the vicinity of this vibrant metropolis. What is that total?\n\n7. Blend your findings from clues 5 and 6 by calculating the absolute difference between the two values you retrieved.\n\n8. Turn your attention to the influential entity that steers the monetary policy of a vast nation — what year marked its establishment?\n\n9. Now, compute the absolute difference of the values from clues 2, 6, and 7, then find the remainder when that result is divided by 10. What single digit do you unveil?",
